Gets event data by a list of event IDs a: Gets event data by a list of event IDs and optional calendar ID to filter.
Comma separated list of event IDs (e.g. '536,525,506,535'). When at least one ID doesn't exist the whole query return a 404 error.
Calendar to filter the events by.
